    • checkAppointmentOverlaps

      public static boolean checkAppointmentOverlaps(Integer customerId, Integer appointmentId, Timestamp startTS, Timestamp endTS)
      Logic to compare appointment times for overlapping appointments for a specific user.
      Parameters:
      customerId - ID of Customer.
      appointmentId - ID of appointment.
      startTS - Timestamp that represents the start of the appointment.
      endTS - Timestamp that represents the end of the appointment.
      Returns:
      A boolean value representing if parameters pass the "overlap" check. False flags mean there are overlaps and the appointments cannot be created.
